# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s26b_cd926e93:

    # Amber "What’s wrong?"
    Amber "Что случилось?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:60
translate spanish hwb_s26b_86b58fd7:

    # "I rush over."
    "Corro hacia ella."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:62
translate spanish hwb_s26b_cd926e93_1:

    # Amber "What’s wrong?"
    Amber "Что произошло?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:64
translate spanish hwb_s26b_b1738642:

    # "Alarm poisons my voice. Did something happen to her after all?"
    "La alarma envenena mi voz. ¿Le pasó algo después de todo?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:66
translate spanish hwb_s26b_2d66be90:

    # "I put my hands on her shoulders and shake her, gently."
    "Pongo mis manos en sus hombros y la sacudo, suavemente."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:68
translate spanish hwb_s26b_c3161cbb:

    # Amber "Marina, talk to me. What happened? Are you okay?"
    Amber "Марина, поговори со мной. Что случилось? Ты в порядке?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:70
translate spanish hwb_s26b_ef4bd15b:

    # "She still can’t talk, but she nods."
    "Todavía no puede hablar, pero asiente."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:72
translate spanish hwb_s26b_469d954d:

    # "Thank God."
    "Gracias a Dios."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:74
translate spanish hwb_s26b_1fcf84d1:

    # "There are no sobs, but her eyes are pouring tears. Every so often she hiccups, like she’s barely restraining herself from fully bawling."
    "No hay sollozos, pero sus ojos están derramando lágrimas. De vez en cuando hipa, como si apenas se contuviera de llorar a gritos."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:76
translate spanish hwb_s26b_f74b691c:

    # Amber "Come on."
    Amber "Пойдем."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:78
translate spanish hwb_s26b_7c89ce28:

    # "I take her hand and lead her back to the RV. No one gives us a second glance. This is probably a common occurrence here."
    "Tomo su mano y la llevo de vuelta a la casa rodante. Nadie nos presta atención. Esto probablemente es algo común aquí."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:80
translate spanish hwb_s26b_1b4a1da6:

    # "Marina silently follows me into the RV."
    "Marina me sigue en silencio dentro de la casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:120
translate spanish hwb_s26b_63034dbe:

    # "I lead her to my bed and have her sit down. I sit beside her."
    "La llevo a mi cama y la hago sentar. Me siento a su lado."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:122
translate spanish hwb_s26b_1f8f3d28:

    # "Alternating between rubbing her back and her shoulders, I try to get her to calm down."
    "Alternando entre frotarle la espalda y los hombros, trato de que se calme."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:124
translate spanish hwb_s26b_cf55a0a1:

    # "Slowly, her breathing slows to normal. When I offer her a tissue, she blows her nose, loudly. Then she takes a few more to wipe her eyes."
    "Lentamente, su respiración vuelve a la normalidad. Cuando le ofrezco un pañuelo, se suena la nariz, ruidosamente. Luego toma unos más para secarse los ojos."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:126
translate spanish hwb_s26b_2f328413:

    # "Rather than prod her more, I wait. Even though it takes all my self-control."
    "En lugar de presionarla más, espero. Aunque me cueste todo mi autocontrol."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:128
translate spanish hwb_s26b_622d2831:

    # "After a shuddery breath, she looks at me, eyes still watering."
    "Tras un respiro tembloroso, me mira, con los ojos aún llorosos."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:130
translate spanish hwb_s26b_a55f84ae:

    # Marina "I messed up, Amber."
    Marina "Я облажалась, Эмбер."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:132
translate spanish hwb_s26b_285ddcc4:

    # Marina "Bad."
    Marina "Сильно."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:137
translate spanish hwb_s26b_937ef0fd:

    # Amber "How?"
    Amber "Как?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:139
translate spanish hwb_s26b_e0c0573e:

    # "Her breath catches again, and she sobs. It’s hoarse and seems to take her by surprise. I immediately rub her shoulders again."
    "Se le corta la respiración otra vez, y solloza. Es ronco y parece tomarla por sorpresa. Inmediatamente le froto los hombros de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s26b_6ee8e76c:

    # "And then there’s a knock at the RV door."
    "Y entonces tocan a la puerta de la casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s26b_99475629:

    # Amber "What the hell?"
    Amber "Какого черта?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s26b_97da4f3f:

    # "I stand up, but I can’t see who it is from here."
    "Me levanto, pero no puedo ver quién es desde aquí."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:153
translate spanish hwb_s26b_7e7e8a8a:

    # Amber "I’ll be right back."
    Amber "Я сейчас вернусь."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:158
translate spanish hwb_s26b_3979106e:

    # "I unlock the front door and open it to an all-too familiar face."
    "Abro la puerta delantera y la abro a una cara demasiado familiar."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:162
translate spanish hwb_s26b_ee0cb9a2:

    # Mariah "It’s time to pay up!"
    Mariah "Пришло время заплатить по счетам!"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:164
translate spanish hwb_s26b_72f8a9a5:

    # "I shut the door."
    "Cierro la puerta."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:170
translate spanish hwb_s26b_fcf12311:

    # "Before it’s even fully latched, Mariah starts to pound on the door."
    "Antes de que esté completamente cerrada, Mariah empieza a golpear la puerta."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:174
translate spanish hwb_s26b_97d08416:

    # "I lock it and head back to Marina."
    "La cierro con llave y vuelvo con Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:176
translate spanish hwb_s26b_64bca316:

    # Marina "Let them in."
    Marina "Впусти их."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:180
translate spanish hwb_s26b_1220824c:

    # Amber "Huh?"
    Amber "Что??"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:182
translate spanish hwb_s26b_5c719008:

    # Marina "Go let them in. It’s Mariah, right?"
    Marina "Пожалуйста, впусти их. Это же Мария, верно?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:184
translate spanish hwb_s26b_8c8959dc:

    # Amber "Yeah, but how did you…"
    Amber "Да, но как ты узн…"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:188
translate spanish hwb_s26b_586edd74:

    # Amber "Wait, does this have something to do with…"
    Amber "Стоп, получается, что она имеет какое-то отношение к…"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:190
translate spanish hwb_s26b_8cca6a15:

    # "Marina nods."
    "Marina asiente."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:192
translate spanish hwb_s26b_9a0ed89a:

    # "With a bad feeling about it all, I go back to the door, which is still suffering Mariah’s assault. I open and step back so they can enter."
    "Con un mal presentimiento sobre todo esto, regreso a la puerta, que aún está sufriendo el asalto de Mariah. La abro y retrocedo para que puedan entrar."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:210
translate spanish hwb_s26b_ab4a1185:

    # "Mariah storms in with a huff, acting like always as if she owns the place."
    "Mariah entra hecha una furia, actuando como siempre, como si el lugar fuera suyo."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:225
translate spanish hwb_s26b_6d25a2fc:

    # "Joseph and Tess file in after her. Joseph gives me a smile and a small shake of the head."
    "Joseph y Tess entran detrás de ella. Joseph me sonríe y niega con la cabeza ligeramente."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:227
translate spanish hwb_s26b_6e114abb:

    # Joseph "Sorry."
    Joseph "Извини."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s26b_c3971709:

    # "He says it so quietly that I don’t think anyone else hears. I figure I’ll find out why he’s apologizing here in a second."
    "Lo dice tan bajo que creo que nadie más lo escucha. Supongo que en un segundo sabré por qué se está disculpando."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s26b_85e5367d:

    # "Like a conqueror, Mariah marches over to Marina and jabs a finger in her face."
    "Como una conquistadora, Mariah camina hacia Marina y le clava un dedo en la cara."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:233
translate spanish hwb_s26b_d4c60369:

    # Mariah "Time to pay up, ditz!"
    Mariah "Пришло время платить по счетам, глупышка!"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:235
translate spanish hwb_s26b_e99a906a:

    # "In two large steps, I move between the two of them."
    "En dos grandes pasos, me pongo entre las dos."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:240
translate spanish hwb_s26b_d08d704d:

    # Amber "Okay, what the hell happened?"
    Amber "Что, черт побери, происходит?!"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s26b_0661e280:

    # Mariah "Didn’t you hear?"
    Mariah "А ты чего, еще не в курсе?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s26b_85564373:

    # Amber "I was about to, when you attacked my front door."
    Amber "Я как раз собиралась это выяснить, когда ты атаковала мою дверь!"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s26b_8a666c3d:

    # Mariah "Well, allow me to deliver the bad news, then!"
    Mariah "Что ж, тогда позволь мне сообщить плохие новости!"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:258
translate spanish hwb_s26b_cf3420df:

    # Tess "Sis stole Marina’s gold."
    Tess "Сестренка украла золото Марины."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:282
translate spanish hwb_s26b_76d84bdb:

    # MariahAmber "{cps=0}What? Did not!{/cps}"
    MariahAmber "{cps=0}Что? Она не могла!{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:295
translate spanish hwb_s26b_dfb31910:

    # "It’s impossible to figure anything out. Marina is crying too hard to talk, and Mariah’s just yelling nonsense like always. I turn to Joe, who’s keeping a safe distance, along with Tess."
    "Es imposible entender nada. Marina llora demasiado fuerte para hablar, y Mariah solo grita tonterías como siempre. Me giro hacia Joe, que se mantiene a una distancia segura, junto con Tess."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:297
translate spanish hwb_s26b_e19e9c67:

    # Amber "Can you please explain?"
    Amber "Пожалуйста, может хоть ты объяснишь что здесь происходит?!"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:299
translate spanish hwb_s26b_7f7d0c9c:

    # Joseph "Sure."
    Joseph "Без проблем."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:301
translate spanish hwb_s26b_8b6d9618:

    # Joseph "Mare ended up making Marina a bet for all the gold, which she lost. It was a pretty silly thing, and I told her to just let it go, but here we are."
    Joseph "Мари заставила Марину сделать ставку на все золото, которое она в итоге потеряла. Это была весьма дурацкая идея, и я говорил ей забить, но как видишь..."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:303
translate spanish hwb_s26b_282ecb98:

    # "I’m equal parts amused and disgusted that Joseph uses the same nickname for Mariah that I do for Marina. Come to think of it, I’m not sure that I ever noticed how similar their names are."
    "Estoy entre divertida y asqueada de que Joseph use el mismo apodo para Mariah que yo para Marina. Pensándolo bien, no estoy segura de haber notado antes lo parecidos que son sus nombres."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:308
translate spanish hwb_s26b_002131db:

    # "Honestly, if we didn’t color their names differently in the text box, I’m pretty sure we’d lose track of who was talking."
    "Honestamente, si no coloreáramos sus nombres de manera diferente en el cuadro de texto, estoy segura de que perderíamos la noción de quién está hablando."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:310
translate spanish hwb_s26b_52643f96:

    # Mariah "A bet’s a bet, and she lost fair and square."
    Mariah "Ставка есть ставка, и она мне по-честному проиграла."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:314
translate spanish hwb_s26b_b9ec317b:

    # Tess "I don’t think it was fair."
    Tess "На самом деле, я не думаю, что это было так уж честно."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:319
translate spanish hwb_s26b_5ac44072:

    # Joseph "The odds were kinda in your favor."
    Joseph "У тебя была ощутимая фора, Мари."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:321
translate spanish hwb_s26b_e924e8c7:

    # "I turn to Marina, the only person whose opinion really matters to me."
    "Me giro hacia Marina, la única persona cuya opinión realmente me importa."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:325
translate spanish hwb_s26b_fb885d2d:

    # Amber "Was it fair?"
    Amber "Все было честно?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:327
translate spanish hwb_s26b_2c80461f:

    # "Slowly, she nods."
    "Lentamente, asiente."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:329
translate spanish hwb_s26b_c3f5e145:

    # Amber "What game did you play?"
    Amber "Во что вы играли?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:331
translate spanish hwb_s26b_8134610a:

    # Marina "Poker."
    Marina "Покер."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:337
translate spanish hwb_s26b_523962c8:

    # "I glare at Mariah, who at least has the shame to look away. Anyone who’s spent more than a minute around Marina would know that there’s no way she could keep a straight face."
    "Fulmino a Mariah, que al menos tiene la vergüenza de mirar hacia otro lado. Cualquiera que haya pasado más de un minuto con Marina sabría que no hay forma de que pueda mantener una cara seria."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:339
translate spanish hwb_s26b_98e89e03:

    # "I sigh, and sit down on the bed beside Marina. I wrap an arm around her. She leans into me, eyes moist."
    "Suspiro y me siento en la cama junto a Marina. La rodeo con un brazo. Ella se apoya en mí, con los ojos húmedos."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:341
translate spanish hwb_s26b_e6c93ebd:

    # Amber "You know you can only take half the treasure, right? Marina and I split it equally, so she couldn’t bet away my half."
    Amber "Вы же знаете, что можете забрать только половину золота, не так ли? Марина и я разделили его поровну, так что она никак не может поставить мою долю."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:345
translate spanish hwb_s26b_eb23a45b:

    # Mariah "That wasn’t the deal."
    Mariah "Эй, уговор был не такой!"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:347
translate spanish hwb_s26b_fddee746:

    # Amber "That’s the only deal she could’ve made."
    Amber "Уж извини, но ничего не поделаешь."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:349
translate spanish hwb_s26b_9871d375:

    # Amber "But."
    Amber "Хотя..."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:353
translate spanish hwb_s26b_9b679453:

    # Amber "I’ll bet you my half against hers."
    Amber "Пожалуй, я поставлю свою долю! Против ее доли, естественно."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:357
translate spanish hwb_s26b_1a052820:

    # Marina "Amber, no!"
    Marina "Эмбер, нет!"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:359
translate spanish hwb_s26b_c051cd0a:

    # "I squeeze her, affectionately, but I shake my head."
    "La aprieto con cariño, pero niego con la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:363
translate spanish hwb_s26b_cc3a3f15:

    # Amber "It’s fine."
    Amber "Все в порядке."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:369
translate spanish hwb_s26b_127ca3a6:

    # "I stand and go to where we’ve been stashing the gold. I pull out the box of nuggets and open it, so Mariah can see."
    "Me levanto y voy a donde hemos estado escondiendo el oro. Saco la caja de pepitas y la abro, para que Mariah pueda ver."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:371
translate spanish hwb_s26b_79940f8b:

    # "Her eyes light up, and she licks her lips."
    "Sus ojos se iluminan y se lame los labios."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:373
translate spanish hwb_s26b_2590b96e:

    # "I snap the box shut."
    "Cierro la caja de golpe."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:377
translate spanish hwb_s26b_06294da8:

    # Mariah "Fine. But we’re not playing poker."
    Mariah "Что ж, отлично! Но мы не будем играть в покер."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:381
translate spanish hwb_s26b_d47b729a:

    # Amber "Oh yeah?"
    Amber "Ох, правда??"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:383
translate spanish hwb_s26b_81d8c0d5:

    # Amber "What game, then?"
    Amber "В таком случае, что это будет за игра?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:387
translate spanish hwb_s26b_5be1439d:

    # "She thinks about it for a moment."
    "Lo piensa por un momento."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:391
translate spanish hwb_s26b_e34f0aca:

    # Mariah "Blackjack."
    Mariah "Блэкджек."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:393
translate spanish hwb_s26b_3c66bf1a:

    # "Seriously? Blackjack is more about luck than it is skill."
    "¿En serio? El blackjack es más cuestión de suerte que de habilidad."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:395
translate spanish hwb_s26b_4185ec4d:

    # "I’m not that great at poker, though. So blackjack might be the most fair game we could play."
    "Aunque no soy tan buena en el póker. Así que el blackjack podría ser el juego más justo que podamos jugar."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:397
translate spanish hwb_s26b_68d6d54a:

    # "I wonder why Mariah suggested it, though. Maybe she expects me to win at poker. If that’s the case, then the mind games have already begun."
    "Me pregunto por qué Mariah lo sugirió, sin embargo. Quizás espera que gane en el póker. Si ese es el caso, entonces los juegos mentales ya han comenzado."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:401
translate spanish hwb_s26b_4271b586:

    # Amber "Fine. It’s a bet."
    Amber "Хорошо. Ставки сделаны."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:405
translate spanish hwb_s26b_92a735ea:

    # "Marina’s stopped crying. Her breath still comes in little spurts, but she’s mostly in control of herself."
    "Marina ha dejado de llorar. Su respiración aún viene en pequeños espasmos, pero se controla en su mayoría."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:407
translate spanish hwb_s26b_5c70c5e9:

    # "She tugs at my shirt."
    "Tira de mi camisa."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:409
translate spanish hwb_s26b_cd7e4920:

    # Marina "Amber, really. You don’t have to do this. I screwed up."
    Marina "Эмбер, серьезно. Ты не должна этого делать! Это же я облажалась..."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:413
translate spanish hwb_s26b_bcdc51cc:

    # Amber "It’s okay, I’ll fix it. That’s what I’m here for, right?"
    Amber "Все хорошо, не волнуйся. Я все исправлю. Для этого я здесь и нахожусь, правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:415
translate spanish hwb_s26b_91ef5353:

    # "I can’t read the look on her face. The one that vanishes after a split second."
    "No puedo descifrar la expresión en su rostro. La que desaparece después de un instante."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:422
translate spanish hwb_s26b_69d7b147:

    # Marina "Okay."
    Marina "Хорошо..."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:424
translate spanish hwb_s26b_d6be1a71:

    # "Facing Mariah again, I put the gold away."
    "Enfrentándome a Mariah de nuevo, guardo el oro."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:428
translate spanish hwb_s26b_cc6dc791:

    # Amber "Where will we play? There’s not enough room here.."
    Amber "Где мы будем играть? Тут недостаточно места..."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:432
translate spanish hwb_s26b_bcd370f9:

    # Mariah "There’s a casino close by, down the street from this one. We can do it there."
    Mariah "Вниз по улице есть казино. Мы можем сделать это там."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:434
translate spanish hwb_s26b_04364470:

    # Amber "I’m not old enough to gamble. Not legally, at least."
    Amber "Боюсь,  я еще недостаточно взрослая, чтобы играть в азартные игры. Законно, по крайней мере."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s26b_3bbca04b:

    # "She shrugs."
    "Se encoge de hombros."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:438
translate spanish hwb_s26b_534cc3e3:

    # Mariah "Doesn’t matter. This place won’t check your ID. Probably gonna be closed down within a year."
    Mariah "Это неважно! В этом месте никто не будет проверять твои документы. Его все равно планируют закрыть в этом году."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s26b_06dd9566:

    # "I don’t like the sound of that. I feel like I’m being set up."
    "No me gusta cómo suena eso. Siento que me están tendiendo una trampa."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:444
translate spanish hwb_s26b_04233a7f:

    # Marina "It’s true. It’s where we played."
    Marina "Это правда. Там мы и играли"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:448
translate spanish hwb_s26b_942becd1:

    # Amber "Really?"
    Amber "Серьезно?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:450
translate spanish hwb_s26b_4742dcb0:

    # Marina "Yeah. They had like, party rooms that were empty. We just used one of those."
    Marina "Ага. У них есть что-то вроде, мм, банкетных залов, которые сейчас пустуют. Мы просто использовали один из них."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:452
translate spanish hwb_s26b_ed3196fe:

    # "I’ve never heard of anything like this place, but if they let Marina in, then they’ll probably let me in, too."
    "Nunca había oído hablar de un lugar como este, pero si dejan entrar a Marina, seguro que a mí también me dejan."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:454
translate spanish hwb_s26b_5c0835d4:

    # "I’d also feel better about playing with cards that I know Mariah won’t have messed with."
    "También me sentiría mejor jugando con cartas que sé que Mariah no habrá manipulado."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:458
translate spanish hwb_s26b_87c5435c:

    # Amber "Fine. Tell me how to get there, and I’ll meet you in a little bit."
    Amber "Отлично. Скажи мне как туда добраться, и чуть позже мы там встретимся."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:460
translate spanish hwb_s26b_de9ab9d0:

    # "She gives me directions as well as the name of the building. Worst case, Marina can probably help find it. Maybe."
    "Me da direcciones y también el nombre del edificio. En el peor de los casos, Marina probablemente pueda ayudar a encontrarlo. Quizás."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:462
translate spanish hwb_s26b_cb0b08c4:

    # "I count at Marina’s half of the gold and put it into one of the boxes before handing to Mariah, who snatches it from my grip."
    "Cuento la mitad del oro de Marina y lo meto en una de las cajas antes de entregárselo a Mariah, que me lo arrebata de las manos."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:468
translate spanish hwb_s26b_be0445c4:

    # Amber "Enjoy, because this is the only time you’ll get to touch the treasure."
    Amber "Наслаждайся, это последний раз, когда ты касаешься моего сокровища."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:480
translate spanish hwb_s26b_6705c88d:

    # "With a final sneer, Mariah leads her troupe out of the RV. Joseph still looks pretty sorry about the whole thing."
    "Con una última mueca de desprecio, Mariah guía a su grupo fuera de la casa rodante. Joseph todavía parece bastante apenado por todo el asunto."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:487
translate spanish hwb_s26b_6d9084c0:

    # "The door slams shut and we’re left in silence."
    "La puerta se cierra de golpe y nos quedamos en silencio."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:489
translate spanish hwb_s26b_77721144:

    # "I look at Marina. She looks at the floor."
    "Miro a Marina. Ella mira al suelo."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:491
translate spanish hwb_s26b_028a0b6f:

    # Marina "I’m really sorry."
    Marina "Я... Мне правда очень жаль..."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:493
translate spanish hwb_s26b_3020b11b:

    # "I’m not even that upset. Compared to all the million and one awful scenarios I’d concocted, this is pretty tame."
    "Ni siquiera estoy tan molesta. Comparado con todos los millones de escenarios horribles que había imaginado, esto es bastante tranquilo."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:495
translate spanish hwb_s26b_6cab12e8:

    # "And knowing Marina, it’s not that shocking, either."
    "Y conociendo a Marina, tampoco es tan impactante."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:497
translate spanish hwb_s26b_92399d9f:

    # "So I’m being honest when I smile at her."
    "Así que soy honesta cuando le sonrío."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:503
translate spanish hwb_s26b_6ac13128:

    # Amber "It’s okay. Really."
    Amber "Все хорошо. Правда.."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:505
translate spanish hwb_s26b_afab8adb:

    # Amber "I’ll go win back your gold, and then we can get outta Vegas."
    Amber "Я отыграю твое золото, и мы уедем из Вегаса."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:509
translate spanish hwb_s26b_692c55a6:

    # "She sniffles."
    "Ella solloza."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:513
translate spanish hwb_s26b_b77ab227:

    # Amber "Seriously though, what were you thinking?"
    Amber "Но если серьезно, то о чем ты только думала?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:515
translate spanish hwb_s26b_24eada0b:

    # Marina "I was just so surprised to see them here! I thought it must be fate or something. I was shopping around and I saw something that I really wanted but I didn’t have enough money."
    Marina "П-понимаешь, я была так удивлена, увидев их всех тут! Я подумала, что это судьба или что-то такое... Понимаешь, просто я ходила по магазинам и заметила одну вещь, которую мне очень хотелось! Но мне не хватало денег..."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:517
translate spanish hwb_s26b_c3505214:

    # Marina "And then I saw the three of them at this little diner so I went in to say hello, and told them all about it."
    Marina "А потом я увидела, что они втроем ужинают тут, и я решила поздороваться и поделиться моей печалью..."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:519
translate spanish hwb_s26b_d6d0d0b9:

    # Amber "What was it you wanted to buy?"
    Amber "А что ты хотела купить?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:523
translate spanish hwb_s26b_22332571:

    # Marina "That’s a secret. I wanted to show it to you."
    Marina "Это секрет. Я хотела сама показать его тебе."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:527
translate spanish hwb_s26b_7407117d:

    # Marina "But anyway, then Mariah made me that bet and I dunno, Amber. I guess I just got so excited about it that I didn’t really think."
    Marina "Но в любом случае... потом Мария предложила мне сделать эту ставку и... я не знаю, Эмбер. Наверное, я была так взволнована, что совсем не думала...."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:529
translate spanish hwb_s26b_a5571b11:

    # Marina "Like if you’d been there you woulda beat her no problem. I don’t even think she’s very good at poker."
    Marina "Мне казалось, что ее можно обыграть без проблем... Я даже не догадывалась, что она может быть настолько хорошим игроком."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:531
translate spanish hwb_s26b_96389e53:

    # Marina "It’s just that… I’m kind of bad at hiding how I feel."
    Marina "Как-то так… А я ведь плохо умею скрывать свои эмоции."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:535
translate spanish hwb_s26b_6e096257:

    # "I can’t help but laugh."
    "No puedo evitar reírme."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:537
translate spanish hwb_s26b_2e357a28:

    # Amber "No way, you’re kidding me!"
    Amber "Быть не может! Ты, наверное, меня разыгрываешь!"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:541
translate spanish hwb_s26b_00505062:

    # "She sticks her tongue out at me. Guess she’s feeling a little bit better."
    "Me saca la lengua. Supongo que se siente un poco mejor."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:545
translate spanish hwb_s26b_5113d4b0:

    # Marina "Really though, what if you lose to Mariah?"
    Marina "Я думаю, а что было бы, если бы ты проиграла Марии?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:549
translate spanish hwb_s26b_3e549ee5:

    # Amber "Then I lose. It won’t happen though."
    Amber "Я бы проиграла и все. В любом случае, этого бы не произошло."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:553
translate spanish hwb_s26b_33aa62f8:

    # Marina "Are you good at blackjack?"
    Marina "Ты хорошо играешь в блэкджек?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:555
translate spanish hwb_s26b_9b328178:

    # Amber "Eh. A lot of it’s luck. There’s stuff you can memorize, like card combos, but I don’t know any of that."
    Amber "Ну, по большей части там нужна только удача. Конечно, там есть вещи вроде карточных комбинаций, но я не знаю их."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:559
translate spanish hwb_s26b_98e83b15:

    # Marina "What if Mariah does?"
    Marina "А что если Мария знает все это?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:561
translate spanish hwb_s26b_02ce8e98:

    # Amber "I doubt it. She would’ve played that against you if she did. Easier to make it seem like you just got unlucky, instead of her taking advantage of you."
    Amber "Хм, сомневаюсь. В таком случае, она бы сыграла с тобой в блэкджек, а не покер. Проще списать все на твою неудачу, чем признать, что она просто нагло воспользовалась тобой."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:565
translate spanish hwb_s26b_de1b9ee3:

    # Marina "She didn’t ta-"
    Marina "Она не восп-"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:569
translate spanish hwb_s26b_72740bdc:

    # Amber "That’s bullshit, Mare. She might not have cheated but she still should’ve known better."
    Amber "Это чушь, Мари. Может она и не мухлевала, но точно знала  о карточных играх больше тебя."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:573
translate spanish hwb_s26b_d85fffab:

    # "Marina frowns and looks at the floor again."
    "Marina frunce el ceño y vuelve a mirar al suelo."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:575
translate spanish hwb_s26b_9cd24031:

    # "I can’t tell if I’m helping or not."
    "No sé si estoy ayudando o no."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:577
translate spanish hwb_s26b_4761f312:

    # "Then I remember the candy I bought her earlier. It had totally slipped my mind over the last hour."
    "Entonces recuerdo los dulces que le compré antes. Se me habían ido completamente de la mente en la última hora."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:581
translate spanish hwb_s26b_7b514a69:

    # Amber "Oh yeah!"
    Amber "О, кстати!"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:583
translate spanish hwb_s26b_aa3f88fb:

    # Amber "I got you something. To try to say sorry for being so weird lately. Even though I’ve already said that, too."
    Amber "У меня есть подарок для тебя! В знак моих извинений за то, что вела себя странно в последнее время. Я знаю, что уже извинялась, но все равно."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:589
translate spanish hwb_s26b_0e4add10:

    # "I grab the bag of chocolates from the fridge and the gummies from above it."
    "Agarro la bolsa de chocolates del refrigerador y las gomitas de arriba."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:591
translate spanish hwb_s26b_4064134c:

    # "Eyes wide, Marina holds them to her like babies."
    "Con los ojos muy abiertos, Marina las sostiene contra sí como si fueran bebés."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:595
translate spanish hwb_s26b_828df7c1:

    # Marina "Amber…"
    Marina "Эмбер…"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:599
translate spanish hwb_s26b_91c448d6:

    # "Her eyes start to water again."
    "Sus ojos empiezan a llenarse de lágrimas otra vez."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:601
translate spanish hwb_s26b_e0b72fbc:

    # Marina "Thank you so much."
    Marina "Огромное спасибо."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:605
translate spanish hwb_s26b_0bbcc428:

    # Amber "Hey, no more crying. This wasn’t supposed to make you cry."
    Amber "Эй, больше никаких слез! Это должно было тебя развеселить, а не заставить рыдать!"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:607
translate spanish hwb_s26b_fa48b584:

    # "She giggles, but that doesn’t stop two tears from running down her face."
    "Ella ríe, pero eso no impide que dos lágrimas le corran por la cara."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:611
translate spanish hwb_s26b_5d232780:

    # Marina "Sorry, I’m crying a lot, huh?"
    Marina "Извини, я слишком много плачу, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:613
translate spanish hwb_s26b_110c7993:

    # Amber "Kinda, yeah."
    Amber "Есть такое."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:615
translate spanish hwb_s26b_0c71e9a6:

    # "Marina laughs again. She unties the gummy bag and digs around in it."
    "Marina vuelve a reír. Desata la bolsa de gomitas y hurga dentro."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:619
translate spanish hwb_s26b_93d37508:

    # Amber "The chocolates got a little melted on the walk back, but they’ve been in the fridge."
    Amber "Шоколадки слегка подтаяли, пока я шла обратно. Но они были в холодильнике."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:623
translate spanish hwb_s26b_293aa285:

    # Marina "They look fine to me!"
    Marina "По-моему они выглядят отлично!"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:625
translate spanish hwb_s26b_16f961b3:

    # "She pulls out a few gummy soda bottles and then offers me the bag."
    "Saca unas cuantas botellitas de gomita con sabor a soda y luego me ofrece la bolsa."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:627
translate spanish hwb_s26b_a5a2667c:

    # "I don’t wanna take too much, but I do find one of the peach rings the cashier recommended."
    "No quiero tomar demasiado, pero encuentro uno de los aros de durazno que la cajera recomendó."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:629
translate spanish hwb_s26b_d28f63a6:

    # "It really is good. Sweet, but in a mild way. It actually tastes like peaches."
    "Es realmente bueno. Dulce, pero de una manera suave. De verdad sabe a durazno."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:633
translate spanish hwb_s26b_d8a25d05:

    # Amber "Are you ready to go?"
    Amber "Ты готова идти?"

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:635
translate spanish hwb_s26b_c9ccac50:

    # "Marina spins the bag to twist it, then ties off the top."
    "Marina gira la bolsa para torcerla y luego ata la parte de arriba."

# game/script/hwb_s26b.rpy:639
translate spanish hwb_s26b_07cc638e:

    # Marina "Yeah."
    Marina "Да."

